1.title: Days Gone By

episode of.title: This Week in Walking Dead (TV Series 2010– )

1.plot: This week Attack of The Show's Chris Gore joins Matt Raub and the rest of the panel as they go over the very first episode of AMC's newest show, The Walking Dead. Also, the team goes over the Kill of the Week and takes a look at some awesome fan titles proposed for the show.

2.title: Guts

episode of.title: This Week in Walking Dead (TV Series 2010– )

2.plot: This week, This Week in Startups host Jason Calacanis joins in the discussion as the gang goes over the events of episode 2, titled "Guts". They also pick a Zombie Kill of the Week and take a sneak peak at episode 3.

3.title: Tell it to the Frogs

episode of.title: This Week in Walking Dead (TV Series 2010– )

3.plot: This week, host Matt Raub is joined once again by Meridith Stokes, G4's Chris Gore, and This Week in Music host Tim Bader, as the gang dissects the happenings in episode 3 of AMC's "The Walking Dead". The gang also decides on a Zombie Kill of the Week and takes a sneak peak at next week's episode.

4.title: Vatos

episode of.title: This Week in Walking Dead (TV Series 2010– )

4.plot: This week, host Matt Raub is joined once again by Meridith Stokes, G4's Chris Gore, and screenwriter Jim Agnew, who is no stranger to zombies, as he's worked with horror legend Dario Argento. This time around, the gang tries to pick up all the pieces of Episode 4, titled "Vatos. There's also another gruesome Zombie Kill of the Week, and Matt brings us a SUPER SECRET sneak peek from next week's episode.

5.title: Wildfire

episode of.title: This Week in Walking Dead (TV Series 2010– )

5.plot: This week, host Matt Raub is joined once again by Meridith Stokes and Jacob Burch as film expert and producer Chris Ullrich stops by along with star of 'The Walking Dead' Andy Rothenberg, who plays Jim on the show. The gang goes over the kill of the week, what's in the CDC, and whether or not Jim will actually become a zombie.

6.title: TS-19

episode of.title: This Week in Walking Dead (TV Series 2010– )

6.plot: This week, host Matt Raub is joined once again by Meridith Stokes and Jacob Burch as "Attack of the Show" host Chris Gore and stand up comedian Jonah Ray join in for a recap of the Season 1 Finale of the show, titled "TS-19". They figure out what's next, ask what the doc whispered to Rick, and talk about a brand new giveaway!

7.title: Season 1 Recap Special

episode of.title: This Week in Walking Dead (TV Series 2010– )

7.plot: This is it, folks. The season is over, and Matt, Meridith, and Jacob welcome their final guests of the season, screenwriter Jim Agnew and This Week in Mobile host Ashley Esqueda. The gang goes over their favorite moments from the season, checks out an awesome compilation video of Every Zombie Death from The Walking Dead by Youtube contributor Eric Linn. They also top off their week long Twitter Giveaway, and get a sneak peek at a new indie zombie comedy, DeadHeads, from the writing/directing team of Drew and Brett Pierce.
